body_html: I see in one of our internal documents that Centos is only supported for version 7 and up. I can't find a public document that addresses this issue, though I suspect it's your problem. If upgrading to Centos 7 is infeasible, you might try on stackoverflow to see whether the community has figured out how to make it work on your version.
